A handy mode for making tables of things.

TabulatedListMode is distributed with Emacs 24 and is used for making the package list in ELPA.

== Use cases ==

* Display lists of things [[https://github.com/nicferrier/emacs-world-time-mode/blob/master/world-time-mode.el#L54|like the world times]] in WorldTime
* Display lists of recent [[https://github.com/stsquad/emacs-mark-tools/blob/master/mark-tools.el|marks]]
* Display lists of resources and enable their management
** like in [[https://github.com/nicferrier/elpakit/blob/master/elpakit.el#L634|Elpakit]]
** and in [[https://github.com/nicferrier/elnode/blob/master/elnode.el#L1252|Elnode]]
